Package: SpecAI.Seg
Type: Package
Title: Hyperspectral Image Segmentation in R!
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Scout Jarman, Zac Rios, Eric Aikens, Kyle Steinicke
Maintainer: Scout Jarman <scout.jarman@usu.edu>
Description: This package is based on the Python package SpecAI.Seg.
    This package provides functionality to download common HSI images, perform
    image segmentation, and plot the resulting segmentation.
